{"tid":355960,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"部ipad唔知咩事","createTime":"2017-08-11T16:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T04:50:49.000Z","uid":41104,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be1c050d692f2d4a2873fb56fbedaad3ee53fdc3","tid":355960,"uid":41104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:39:18.000Z","msg":"話說我一向都淨係用部ipad mini黎save相同睇片<br />\n琴晚唔做咩事睇睇下youtube自己重新開機<br />\n之後就去番好似買新機個介面<br />\n然後叫我入翻apple account<br />\n<br />\n問題就黎啦<br />\n<br />\n我入黎入去，佢都話我個密碼錯<br />\n(ID同密碼我一向都記得好清楚一定唔會有問題)<br />\n如是者我唯有撳忘記密碼，用個email黎認証<br />\n奇怪嘅係我用@icloud.com黎做email同ID<br />\n但佢話我個認證嘅email係@stabifix.com<br />\n我完全唔知stabifix係乜春，更加無用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最有問題係佢話有人用 尋找iPhone 黎揾我部機<br />\n而我肯定我有熄左依個功能 (有apple嘅 email 確認)<br />\n<br />\n所以想問有冇人知道我部ipad係發生咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋點先可以解番部機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f81d9287f91fa075b257d9f3c8ada9ea21d673","tid":355960,"uid":67026,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:40:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">俾</span>"},{"pid":"d75b666b946fc5299080122631d57d45bd3e1b5c","tid":355960,"uid":97814,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:40:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cca095091e30646d85dab45191d11187ca2c685","tid":355960,"uid":41104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:41:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>畀返部機人啦</blockquote><br />\n部機真係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25cca4253b9d7d0e523cb2a95cd7b12f821f08cc","tid":355960,"uid":46616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:46: